---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const meta = {
  title: 'Durable Review 2025: AI Website Builder for Small Businesses',
  description: 'Durable is AI-powered website builder for small businesses. Generate complete website in 30 seconds. AI writes copy, selects images, builds pages. Not for complex sites. Free 3-day trial. From $15/month. Best for solopreneurs, service businesses, local businesses.',
  image: '/og-image.svg',
  keywords: ['Durable review', 'AI website builder', 'Durable pricing', 'website generator', 'small business website'],
};
---

<Layout {...meta}>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#10B981]/5 to-[#059669]/5 py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-black text-[#10B981] mb-4 tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">
        AI Tool Review · 2025 Updated
      </p>

      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">
        Durable Review
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
        Durable is an AI-powered website builder specifically for small businesses. Answer a few questions about your business, AI generates a complete website in 30 seconds. Copy, images, pages - all created instantly. Not for complex websites or developers. Built for solopreneurs who need a site fast without hiring anyone.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          Quick answer: Durable is excellent if you need a basic small business website immediately. AI generates something usable in seconds. The copy is surprisingly good. Design is clean but limited. Not for complex sites, e-commerce, or developers. Use Durable for MVP or temporary site, upgrade to proper builder when you grow.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What It Is -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      What Durable Is (and Isn't)
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">What Durable Does</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Generates complete websites:</strong> AI builds entire site from business description</li>
          <li>• <strong>Writes copy:</strong> Creates headlines, descriptions, services pages</li>
          <li>• <strong>Selects images:</strong> Chooses relevant stock photos</li>
          <li>• <strong>Builds multiple pages:</strong> Home, about, services, contact</li>
          <li>• <strong>Fast:</strong> 30-second website generation</li>
          <li>• <strong>Includes business tools:</strong> CRM, invoicing, AI assistant</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">What Durable Doesn't Do</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Not for complex sites:</strong> Limited customization options</li>
          <li>• <strong>No e-commerce:</strong> Can't sell products online</li>
          <li>• <strong>Not developer-friendly:</strong> No code access, limited export</li>
          <li>• <strong>Design constraints:</strong> Templates are structured, not flexible</li>
          <li>• <strong>Platform locked:</strong> Hosting and editing stay on Durable</li>
          <li>• <strong>Small business focused:</strong> That's the use case, intentionally</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Durable Pricing
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Free Trial (3 Days)</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Price:</strong> Free for 3 days</li>
          <li>• <strong>Full access:</strong> Test all features</li>
          <li>• <strong>Credit card required:</strong> Yes, for trial</li>
          <li>• <strong>Auto-bills:</strong> Converts to paid if not cancelled</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Value:</strong> Generous trial to test if Durable fits your needs. Just remember to cancel if not needed.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Starter ($15/month or $150/year)</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Website builder:</strong> AI-generated website</li>
          <li>• <strong>Custom domain:</strong> Use your own domain</li>
          <li>• <strong>AI assistant:</strong> AI writing helper</li>
          <li>• <strong>Invoicing:</strong> Basic invoicing tools</li>
          <li>• <strong>CRM:</strong> Basic customer management</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Value:</strong> Fair pricing for what you get. Most solopreneurs will want Starter for custom domain and business tools.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Business ($25/month or $250/year)</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Everything in Starter, plus:</strong></li>
          <li>• <strong>Multi-page website:</strong> Up to 10 pages</li>
          <li>• <strong>AI blog writer:</strong> Generate blog posts</li>
          <li>• <strong>SEO tools:</strong> Basic optimization features</li>
          <li>• <strong>Analytics:</strong> Visitor tracking</li>
          <li>• <strong>Priority support:</strong> Faster help</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Value:</strong> Worth the upgrade if you need more pages or want content marketing features.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-orange-50 border-2 border-orange-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">MO ($100/month or $1,000/year)</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Everything in Business, plus:</strong></li>
          <li>• <strong>Unlimited pages:</strong> No page limit</li>
          <li>• <strong>White label:</strong> Remove Durable branding</li>
          <li>• <strong>Multiple websites:</strong> Up to 3 sites</li>
          <li>• <strong>Dedicated support:</strong> Priority assistance</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Value:</strong> For agencies or multiple businesses. Most solopreneurs won't need this tier.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Features -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Key Features
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">1. AI Website Generation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Answer a few questions about your business. Durable generates a complete website in 30 seconds.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Business description:</strong> What you do, who you serve</li>
          <li>• <strong>Location:</strong> Where you're based (for local businesses)</li>
          <li>• <strong>Name and industry:</strong> Basic business info</li>
          <li>• <strong>AI generates:</strong> Complete site with copy and images</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Getting a website live typically takes weeks. Durable makes it 30 seconds. The AI-generated copy is surprisingly decent for small businesses.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">2. Business Tools Included</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Durable isn't just a website builder. It includes tools to run your business.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>CRM:</strong> Track customers and leads</li>
          <li>• <strong>Invoicing:</strong> Create and send invoices</li>
          <li>• <strong>AI assistant:</strong> Help with writing and tasks</li>
          <li>• <strong>Analytics:</strong> Track visitors and performance</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Most small businesses need these tools anyway. Having them integrated saves time and money compared to separate subscriptions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">3. AI Blog Writer</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Generate blog posts with AI to improve SEO and attract customers.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Topic suggestions:</strong> AI suggests blog topics</li>
          <li>• <strong>Content generation:</strong> Writes full blog posts</li>
          <li>• <strong>SEO optimized:</strong> Includes keywords and structure</li>
          <li>• <strong>Edit and refine:</strong> You can tweak AI-generated content</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Content marketing drives traffic but takes time. AI assistance makes it feasible for busy solopreneurs.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">4. Simple Editor</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Edit your generated site with a simple, intuitive editor.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Click to edit:</strong> Click any text to change it</li>
          <li>• <strong>Drag and drop:</strong> Move sections around</li>
          <li>• <strong>Replace images:</strong> Swap out photos easily</li>
          <li>• <strong>Add sections:</strong> Include testimonials, services, etc.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> AI gets you 80% there. The editor lets you customize the last 20% to match your brand and voice.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Use Cases -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Who Durable Is For
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">✅ Perfect For</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Solopreneurs:</strong> Consultants, coaches, freelancers needing quick web presence</li>
          <li>• <strong>Service businesses:</strong> Plumbers, electricians, cleaners, local services</li>
          <li>• <strong>Small business MVP:</strong> Test business idea with minimal investment</li>
          <li>• <strong>Temporary sites:</strong> Landing page while building proper site</li>
          <li>• <strong>Non-technical users:</strong> People who can't code and don't want to learn</li>
          <li>• <strong>Speed-first:</strong> Anyone needing a site today, not next month</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">❌ Not For</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>E-commerce:</strong> Can't sell products online</li>
          <li>• <strong>Complex websites:</strong> Limited customization and features</li>
          <li>• <strong>Content-heavy sites:</strong> Blogs, publishers, media sites</li>
          <li>• <strong>Developers:</strong> No code access, limited export options</li>
          <li>• <strong>Full control:</strong> Want complete design freedom</li>
          <li>• <strong>Scalable businesses:</strong> Fast-growing companies need flexible platforms</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pros and Cons -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Pros and Cons
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Pros</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Incredibly fast:</strong> Website in 30 seconds</li>
          <li>• <strong>Good AI copy:</strong> Surprisingly decent writing</li>
          <li>• <strong>Includes business tools:</strong> CRM, invoicing, AI assistant</li>
          <li>• <strong>Easy to use:</strong> No technical skills needed</li>
          <li>• <strong>Affordable:</strong> $15/month is reasonable</li>
          <li>• <strong>All-in-one:</strong> Website + business tools together</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Cons</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Limited customization:</strong> Can't fully customize design</li>
          <li>• <strong>No e-commerce:</strong> Can't sell products</li>
          <li>• <strong>Platform locked:</strong> Hosting and editing stay on Durable</li>
          <li>• <strong>Basic designs:</strong> Templates look generic</li>
          <li>• <strong>No code access:</strong> Can't edit HTML/CSS</li>
          <li>• <strong>Scalability limits:</strong> Outgrows quickly for successful businesses</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Alternatives -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Alternatives to Consider
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Wix</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>For:</strong> More flexibility and features</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>Price:</strong> Free or $16/month</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">More templates, more customization, app marketplace. Not AI-generated but more powerful long-term.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Squarespace</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>For:</strong> Beautiful design and simplicity</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>Price:</strong> $16/month</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Designer templates, cleaner interface. Better for brands that care about aesthetics. Not AI-powered.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Framer</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>For:</strong> Modern design and CMS</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>Price:</strong> Free or $16/month</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Visual builder with CMS. More flexible than Durable. Better if you want to grow beyond basic site.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">WordPress</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>For:</strong> Unlimited flexibility</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>Price:</strong> Free (self-hosted)</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Most flexible option. Can do anything but requires setup and maintenance. Overkill for simple sites.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom Line -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black mb-6">Bottom Line</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">Durable fills a specific niche: AI-generated websites for small businesses who need something fast. If that's what you need, it delivers. The AI-generated copy is decent. The business tools are useful. But it's not a long-term solution for growing businesses.</p>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6"><strong>Use Durable if:</strong></p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
        <li>• You need a website today, not next week</li>
        <li>• You're a solopreneur or service business</li>
        <li>• You don't want to learn website building</li>
        <li>• You need basic business tools (CRM, invoicing)</li>
        <li>• You're okay with limited customization</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6"><strong>Skip Durable if:</strong></p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
        <li>• You need e-commerce functionality</li>
        <li>• You want complete design control</li>
        <li>• You're a developer who wants code access</li>
        <li>• You're building a content-heavy site</li>
        <li>• You expect rapid growth and scalability</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700"><strong>Bottom line:</strong> Start with the free trial. If Durable gets you 80% of the way there, $15/month is reasonable for Starter. Plan to migrate to Wix, Squarespace, Framer, or WordPress when you outgrow it. Durable is a starting point, not a forever home.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-6 text-gray-900">
      Related Reviews
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <a href="/v0-review" class="block bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">v0.dev Review</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">AI React code generator</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/bento-review" class="block bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Bento Review</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">AI portfolio builder</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
